milestones.description: Constant has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (12) as an umpire, going past Dickie Bird
Chris Old has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (23), going past Tony Greig
Bob Taylor has broken the record for most dismissals (17) in ODIs for ENG, going past Alan Knott's 16
Chris Old has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (23) for ENG, going past Tony Greig
Graham Gooch and Mike Brearley's 108-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 105 between Clive Radley and David Gower
